<text>This is a list of notable [[Rastafari movement|Rastafari]].

==Early teachers==
*Leonard Howell
*Joseph Hibbert
*Archibald Dunkley
*Sam Brown
*Vernon Carrington
*Charles Edwards
*Mortimer Planner

